  "Description": {
    "English": "An advanced, self-regulating hybrid material, the Cryo-Pump distributes heat across itself with near perfect efficiency, making it vital in the creation of thermal regulators.<br><br>Crafted from <span class=\"name name-technology\">Hot Ice</span> and <span class=\"name name-fuel\">Thermic Condensate</span>",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "冷沉淀泵是一种高级自制的混合材料，可以接近完美的效率分配热量，对于热调节器的制作至关重要。<br><br>由<span class=\"name name-technology\">热冰</span>和<span class=\"name name-fuel\">热凝物</span>制作。",
    "TencentChinese": "冷沉淀泵是一种高级自制的混合材料，可以接近完美的效率分配热量，对于热调节器的制作至关重要。<br><br>由<span class=\"name name-technology\">热冰</span>和<span class=\"name name-fuel\">热凝物</span>制作。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "低溫泵為先進自體調節混合材料，能夠以近乎完美的效率分配自身熱能，因此製造熱能調節器時相當重要。<br><br>可使用<span class=\"name name-technology\">炎冰</span>與<span class=\"name name-fuel\">導熱凝液</span>製造。"
  },
