    "English": "Craft from <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">gas-based</span> products: <span class=\"name name-commodity\">Hot Ice</span> and <span class=\"name name-commodity\">Thermic Condensate</span>.<br>Learn the relevant blueprints by raiding <span class=\"name name-technology\">planetary factories</span> or from the <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Synthesis Lab</span> on the <span class=\"name name-special\">Space Anomaly</span>.",
